{"tid":2059311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"怕資金撤走　口交部溫和澄清「謬論」","createTime":"2020-06-10T23:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T08:59:05.000Z","uid":227445,"like":20,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"aa1ab4c2042a9bed81e3b4461ca938c4b2060239","tid":2059311,"uid":227445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T23:31:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VDIYa4S8mQ0CfsWCN8xfeGkNlnQ=/802x659/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N3FOOMHSN2FQSYXSJ4FFSD7BWM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVDIYa4S8mQ0CfsWCN8xfeGkNlnQ%3D%2F802x659%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN3FOOMHSN2FQSYXSJ4FFSD7BWM.jpg&h=dc7c857f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國外交部昨在網站撰文澄清「六個謬論」。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】世界各國紛紛表態反對港版國安法立法，中國外交部昨在網站撰文澄清「六個謬論」，聲稱網上謔稱「美軍來了我帶路」言論已嚴重危害國家主權；文章又提出澳門立法後GPD和遊客數量有增長。有學者指出，聲明措詞比以往溫和，但「唔係可憐香港人，係唔想走資，唔想美國打香港牌施壓。」<br />\n<br />\n外交部用近3,000字交代「事實真相」，措詞有別以往「戰狼作風」，例如「外部勢力干預」一詞只出現三次，文章亦無點名批評西方政要。中國問題專家林和立指出，文章以溫和態度游說，對內要安撫香港人不要走資，對外則希望西方不要撤資。但他認為外交部做法成效有限，「任何熟悉中國政策嘅人都知，中國要全面控制香港」。「新冷戰」氣氛已經形成，美國結合其他盟友向中方施壓，林和立認為外交部的目的是拉攏歐盟親中成員國，向他們說明國安法沒有破壞香港<br />\n<br />\n口交部全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/zyxw/t1787597.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fmprc.gov.cn%2Fweb%2Fzyxw%2Ft1787597.shtml&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=50703c24\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fmprc.gov.cn/web/zyxw/t1787597.shtml</a><br />\n法治。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200611/ID4P52XX6YGAV47A2DEEDYT7K4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200611%2FID4P52XX6YGAV47A2DEEDYT7K4%2F&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRD2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=487cffb3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200611%2FID4P52XX6YGAV47A2DEEDYT7K4%2F&h=59dfe729\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200611/ID4P52XX6YGAV47A2DEEDYT7K4/</a>"},{"pid":"5cfc011ee3df665007c2863cb175afc33237f4e2","tid":2059311,"uid":41366,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T23:33:17.000Z","msg":"姐係謬論係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a866edd7bf29c950890bf181a82882e3bd360117","tid":2059311,"uid":78819,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T23:36:21.000Z","msg":"啲共式中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咩咩咩六個XXX 三個不"},{"pid":"bc60060870c90e82f8355dbab8304f8b62bbec6c","tid":2059311,"uid":78971,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T23:36:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">芝麻人冇合約精神</span></span><br />\n講咩都嘥氣<br />\n<br />\n應承咗做唔出<br />\n冇傾過嘅就格硬嚟"},{"pid":"31db08334fa500187665279afdb1a982dc898805","tid":2059311,"uid":32675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5cfc011ee3df665007c2863cb175afc33237f4e2","tid":2059311,"uid":41366,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T23:33:17.000Z","msg":"姐係謬論係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T23:36:39.000Z","msg":"中共反駁既通常都係真,好人好姐點會比人屈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0589a762d948dc63ed1f1c8021d6ed1a15359d","tid":2059311,"uid":274996,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T23:37:08.000Z","msg":"中國既紀錄太差，完全不可信，一切都係信任問題，正如中國疫苗同德國疫苗都係疫苗，但你信邊個？"},{"pid":"0d76cbae7553f4178b152b93fd7fa885b196f642","tid":2059311,"uid":274996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T23:38:36.000Z","msg":"而且佢夾硬用附件3 立法係破壞一國兩制。以為佢都可以用呢招亂Q 咁幫香港立法"},{"pid":"ebff5b3ca105c32e191a34cd8cfd3987e9e4a685","tid":2059311,"uid":254450,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T23:41:47.000Z","msg":"個網左上角外交部三隻字鬼畫符咁，點解支那狗咁撚鐘意寫呢種咁核特嘅書法字，支那人d美學真係特別差<img